《看門狗》普遍獲得了正面回應，在它主打的強項中，評論列舉了駭客攻擊的元素、各種任務和線上多人遊戲模式, 不過實際遊戲畫質被大幅縮水也被招來批評。[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]分別給了PlayStation 4版83％和82/100<ref name="GR-PS4" /><ref name="MC-PS4" />，Xbox One版為78％和78/100<ref name="GR-XONE" /><ref name="MC-XONE" />，Microsoft Windows版本為77％和81/100的分數<ref name="GR-PC" /><ref name="MC-PC" />。而Xbox 360和PlayStation 3版本的遊戲目前都尚未給分<ref name="GR-360">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/673018-watch-dogs/index.html |title=Watch Dogs for Xbox 360 |work=[[GameRankings|GameRankings]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2014-05-27 |archive-date=2019-12-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209011949/https://www.gamerankings.com/xbox360/673018-watch-dogs/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MC-360">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-360/watch-dogs |title=Watch Dogs for Xbox 360 Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2014-05-27 |archive-date=2017-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012124142/http://www.metacritic.com/game/xbox-360/watch-dogs |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="GR-PS3"/><ref name="MC-PS3">{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/watch-dogs |title=Watch Dogs for PlayStation 3 Reviews |work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2014-05-27 |archive-date=2018-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180610212253/http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/watch-dogs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

審稿人稱讚了遊戲的駭客入侵元素。《[[Game_Informer|Game Informer]]》的Jeff Marchiafava和[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]網站的Kevin VanOrd兩人都特別注意到它已改善了戰鬥系統<ref name="GameInformer review"/><ref name="GameSpot review"/>。[[IGN|IGN]]的Dan Stapleton稱最具特點的遊戲之一<ref name="IGN review"/>。《[[Metro|Metro]]》的Ludwig Kietzmann稱入侵方式為「精緻、可靠和準確」，並相信遊戲內的特色提高了整個遊戲整體的水平<ref name="Metro review"/>。而[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的Chris Carter则覺得這駭客功能少使人印象深刻，表示「育碧蒙特婁幾乎沒有什麼革命性的目標要我們去思考」<ref name="Destructoid review">{{cite web |last=Carter |first=Chris |date=2014-05-27 |url=http://www.destructoid.com/review-watch-dogs-275336.phtml |title=Review: Watch Dogs |publisher=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]] |accessdate=2014-05-27 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226222255/https://www.destructoid.com/review-watch-dogs-275336.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

爭議是在遊戲發布的一個月前引起，因為育碧被人發現在一個公關活動上，分別給予免費遊戲新聞記者一台[[Nexus_7|Nexus 7]]的平板電腦作為禮物，已經被許多人視為賄賂行為，以努力提高遊戲的審查成績，和被指控圖像優質售後服務的謊言等負面新聞<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.incgamers.com/2014/04/ubisoft-admits-giving-nexus-7-tablets-journalists-watch-dogs-event |title=Ubisoft admits giving Nexus 7 tablets to journalists at Watch Dogs event {{!}} IncGamers.com<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2014-06-03 |archive-date=2014-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140528070211/http://www.incgamers.com/2014/04/ubisoft-admits-giving-nexus-7-tablets-journalists-watch-dogs-event |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

另外，為了通過日本[[CERO|CERO]]審查，亞洲區(中、台、港、澳、日)版本的遊戲系統被修改：
1.在蜘蛛戰車數位旅成模式中，殺害市民之行為將由加分改為扣分
2. 遊戲角色波比（Poppy）之半裸畫面變更為穿戴胸罩
3. 人口販子拍賣會上之女子之半裸畫面變更為穿戴胸罩。

此舉引發亞洲區的玩家不滿。

=== 銷售 ===
《看門狗》打破了育碧史上最大的首日銷量紀錄<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-05-28-watch-dogs-sold-more-than-any-ubisoft-game-ever-in-24-hours|title=Watch Dogs outsold any Ubisoft game ever in 24 hours|last=Matulef|first=Jeffrey|date=2014-05-28|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|publisher=Gamer Network|accessdate=2014-05-28|archive-date=2014-05-28|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140528215634/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-05-28-watch-dogs-sold-more-than-any-ubisoft-game-ever-in-24-hours|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《看門狗》亦擊敗了英國[[知識產權|IP]]銷售額紀錄保持者《[[黑色洛城|黑色洛城]]》。總體而言，《看門狗》是英國推出的17大遊戲之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-02-watch-dogs-is-the-biggest-new-ip-launch-in-the-uk-ever|title=Watch Dogs the biggest new IP launch in the UK ever|last=Phillips|first=Tom|date=2014-06-02|work=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]|publisher=Gamer Network|accessdate=2014-06-02|archive-date=2014-06-02|archive-url=https://archive.is/20140602093538/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-06-02-watch-dogs-is-the-biggest-new-ip-launch-in-the-uk-ever|dead-url=no}}</ref>。遊戲在發佈一周後，已於世界各地售出逾400万套遊戲。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.vg247.com/2014/06/03/watch-dogs-sells-4-million-in-first-week/ |title=Watch Dogs sells 4 million in first week |last=Martin |first=Matt |publisher=[[VG247|VG247]] |date=2014-06-03 |accessdate=2014-06-03 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129112306/https://www.vg247.com/2014/06/03/watch-dogs-sells-4-million-in-first-week/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

